ingredients: ["cream cheese", "crabmeat", "cocktail sauce"]
directions: ["In a dish, place rolled, oblong cream cheese.", "Then put crabmeat all over this (pretty thick).", "Then pour cocktail sauce over meat.", "Serve with crackers."]

title: Carrots Lyonnaise
ingredients: ["1 lb. carrots, cut in julienne strips", "2 cubes chicken bouillon", "water to cover", "1/4 c. margarine", "1 to 3 onions, sliced", "1 Tbsp. flour"]
